---
title: Creamy Roasted Vegetable Curry with Mini Naans
description: Full of delicious, wholesome ingredients like roasted sweet potato and cauliflower, our creamy roasted vegetable curry is like a big, warm hug on a cold day. Our mini garlic naan is perfect for wiping up the leftovers in the bowl because trust us, you’ll want every last bit of this recipe!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-roasted-vegetable-curry-46a98c43-5f7c544a.jpg
